        "date": "2025-06-14",
        "author": "Token Mallick",
        "imageUrl": "https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEg992AC7ELAnagJ1RIqeuMckJ4grZKKprmAj2X_EZjEFvUV6oZJJ2VgWJ06IwIe9fs32zAl-LaUosWBwi_dK6OmeaRt1cbR9gUDGVgqwvRJV26D1UGgOemiGzQCa6xFuXqrq8xhEN8zR-zuppsktMSkc9oU7LM9X3OApPtzYMW9c16vDhgSU5eXeEMViPp7/s800/ChatGPT%20Image%20Jun%208,%202025,%2008_20_37%20PM.png"
