        "author": "Token Mallick",
        "imageUrl": "https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhYa0qJCNjFzj2uHCUYe9b6TiHO49HCUOFf7bFGyAlgyXlFotdcUIVHx5fUtA2YrJAVuDq0RS9lQ8W_M1AeOq6JTQB5tTO_D6q_go_IKe257c9Kdu4AZEKexQbUXBsW3tunnOOh0Mn2C6-vDBVB52U6NNrvn-mWhbPexzNOiSTQjJC6vLtFH0JgBYcK4ZMw/s800/ChatGPT%20Image%20May%2025,%202025,%2011_38_48%20AM.png"
